                     (See strategy-consulting/NOTICE for additional notices.)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. marketing/      — from "claude-marketing-research-skill"
                     Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. product-management/ — from "pm-skills-starter-pack"
                     No license specified by the upstream pack. Used here as
                     provided; consult the original author before redistribution.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Each folder remains subject to its respective upstream license. Where a folder
is governed by the Apache License 2.0, you must comply with its terms,
including retention of notices. Where governed by the MIT License, the standard
MIT permission and warranty-disclaimer terms apply.


